                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-58-defend589 t17960217-58-punish339"></join>
               Fined 1s.
            </rs> and <rs id="t17960217-58-punish340" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960217-58-punish340" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960217-58-punish340" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="houseOfCorrection"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-58-defend589 t17960217-58-punish340"></join>
               confined in the House of Correction six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second London Jury, before Mr. Justice LAWRENCE.</p>
